org.ejbca.core.protocol.ws.client.gen

Class RevokeStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ejbca.core.protocol.ws.client.gen.RevokeStatus

  • public class RevokeStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used when checking the revocation status of a certificate. Contains the following data: IssuerDN CertificateSN (hex) RevokationDate Reason (One of the REVOKATION_REASON constants)
